## Usage

### Minimal

```terraform
resource "system_group" "fileshare" {
  name = "fileshare"
}
```

### Explicit gid

```terraform
resource "system_group" "fileshare" {
  name = "fileshare"
  gid  = 1001
}
```

### System group

```terraform
resource "system_group" "nginx" {
  name   = "nginx"
  system = true
}
```

### System group with explicit gid

```terraform
resource "system_group" "nginx" {
  name   = "nginx"
  gid    = 201
  system = true
}
```

